4) You can never run fast enough, even if you are just popping to the shop. <br>
3) People are accutely unaware of approaching cars until you have either ground them into the tarmac or until the very last moment and they dive out of the way. <br>
2) If you are going to keep something safe, lock it, trap it, guard it and put it behind some locked trapped guards in a lock trapped dungeon - preferably with some guards especially if you live in a town. <br>
