<br>
Female hedgehogs are pink and carry very large mallets.<br>
<br>
Hedgehogs are faster than cars.<br>
<br>
Hedgehogs have snappy red tennies.<br>
<br>
Hedgehogs have a fetish for large emeralds.<br>
<br>
Large red gems are not rubies. They're emeralds. Don't ask why, they just are.<br>
<br>
Hedgehogs don't need a reason to save the world from egg-shaped maniacs: it's in their nature. That and foraging for berries and whatnot.<br>
<br>
